    "updated_at": "2019-04-02T03:55:10Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It looks like `Repairable.ResolveOrder` is manually wrangling/mangling activities - moving all the the move-to/carryall stuff inside the `Resupply` activity (or a new activity) will bring this in line with our best practice, and queuing them as children instead of top-level activities will fix the ordering issues.\r\n\r\nThis may be best left to a separate PR, since this is all aside from the main goal here."
